                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240114-82-victim803 t18240114-82-viclabel474"></join>, and live at Blackheath. On the 4th of December, I left my cart opposite Mr. Kimber's, in <placeName id="t18240114-82-crimeloc475">Bishopsgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18240114-82-crimeloc475" type="placeName" value="Bishopsgate-street"></interp>
